    "topic": "Identifying the Pattern",
    "subtopics": [
      {
        "subtopic": "How to Analyze",
        "content": "1. Check for common difference\n2. Check for multiplication/division\n3. Try square/cube of natural numbers\n4. Look for alternate terms\n5. Check difference between differences\n\n**Example:**\nSeries: 1, 4, 9, 16, ? → Pattern: n² → 1², 2², 3², 4² ⇒ Next: 5² = 25"
